of any unauthorized use of your account. We are not liable for any losses resulting from failure to protect your information.",privacy:"Privacy and Data Protection",privacyContent:"We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data in accordance with our privacy policy. We may collect and use your information to provide services and improve your app experience.",payment:"Payment and Billing",paymentContent:"All payments are processed through secure channels. We accept cash on delivery and electronic payments. Prices are subject to change without prior notice. Payments are non-refundable except in specific cases.",liability:"Liability and Warranties",liabilityContent:"We provide the service as is without express or implied warranties. We will not be liable for any direct or indirect damages resulting from app usage. The user assumes full responsibility for their use of the app.",termination:"Service Termination",terminationContent:"Either party may terminate this agreement at any time. We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account if you violate these terms. Upon termination, all services will cease immediately.",changes:"Terms Modification",changesContent:"We reserve the right to modify these terms and conditions at any time. You will be notified of any significant changes. Continued use of the app after modifications means you agree to the new terms."}},contactUs:{title:"Contact Us",welcomeTitle:"We're here to help",welcomeSubtitle:"Contact us anytime and we'll be happy to assist you",contactMethodsTitle:"Contact Methods",formTitle:"Send us a message",responseTime:"We usually respond within 24 hours",methods:{email:"Email",emailSubtitle:"support@pharmacy.com",phone:"Phone",phoneSubtitle:"+1 234 567 8900",whatsapp:"WhatsApp",whatsappSubtitle:"+1 234 567 8900"},form:{email:"Email",emailPlaceholder:"Enter your email",title:"Message Title",titlePlaceholder:"Enter message title",message:"Message",messagePlaceholder:"Write your message here...",submit:"Send Message"},errors:{emailRequired:"Email is required",emailInvalid:"Invalid email format",titleRequired:"Message title is required",titleTooShort:"Title is too short (minimum 5 characters)",messageRequired:"Message is required",messageTooShort:"Message is too short (minimum 10 characters)"},success:{title:"Message Sent Successfully",message:"Thank you! Your message has been sent successfully. We'll get back to you as soon as possible.",button:"OK"},error:{title:"Sending Error",message:"An error occurred while sending the message. Please try again."}},aboutUs:{title:"About Us",welcomeTitle:"Welcome to Digital Pharmacy World",welcomeSubtitle:"We provide the best technological solutions for pharmacists and customers",ourStory:"Our Story",description:"Pharmacy app is an advanced digital platform that aims to connect pharmacists with customers and facilitate the ordering and delivery process. We believe that technology can make healthcare more accessible and convenient for everyone.",whyChooseUs:"Why Choose Us?",ourNumbers:"Our Numbers Speak",ourTeam:"Our Team",mission:"Our Mission",missionText:"We aim to transform the pharmacy experience through advanced technology, making medicines and healthcare accessible to everyone with ease and safety.",vision:"Our Vision",visionText:"To be the leading platform in digital pharmacy in the region, providing innovative solutions that contribute to improving the quality of healthcare.",followUs:"Follow Us",contactEmail:"info@pharmacy.com",contactPhone:"+1 234 567 8900",contactAddress:"Technology Street, Health City, Care Country",features:{secure:"Secure & Safe",secureDesc:"Complete protection for your data and personal information",fast:"Fast & Efficient",fastDesc:"Fast and reliable service at all times",reliable:"Reliable & Available",reliableDesc:"24/7 service with professional support team",caring:"Caring & Supportive",caringDesc:"We care about your health and provide the best care"},stats:{users:"Active Users",pharmacies:"Partner Pharmacies",orders:"Completed Orders",satisfaction:"Satisfaction Rate"},team:{ceo:"Ahmed Mohammed",ceoPosition:"Chief Executive Officer",cto:"Sarah Ahmed",ctoPosition:"Chief Technology Officer",cmo:"Mohammed Ali",cmoPosition:"Chief Marketing Officer"}},faq:{title:"FAQ",welcomeTitle:"Welcome to Help Center",welcomeSubtitle:"Find answers to your common questions",categoriesTitle:"Categories",questionsTitle:"Frequently Asked Questions",questions:"question",needHelp:"Need additional help?",contactUs:"Contact us and we'll be happy to help you",categories:{all:"All",general:"General",account:"Account",orders:"Orders",payment:"Payment",technical:"Technical"},general:{question1:"How can I create a new account?",answer1:"You can create a new account by clicking the \"Create Account\" button on the login page, then follow the required steps to enter your personal information.",question2:"How can I reset my password?",answer2:"You can reset your password by clicking \"Forgot Password\" on the login page, then follow the instructions sent to your email."},account:{question1:"How can I update my personal information?",answer1:"You can update your personal information by going to account settings and modifying the required information, then save the changes.",question2:"How can I delete my account?",answer2:"You can delete your account by going to account settings and selecting \"Delete Account\" option, keeping in mind that this action cannot be undone."},orders:{question1:"How can I track my order?",answer1:"You can track your order by going to \"My Orders\" section and selecting the desired order, where you'll find order status details and current location.",question2:"How can I cancel an order?",answer2:"You can cancel your order by going to \"My Orders\" section and selecting the desired order, then clicking \"Cancel Order\" if it's still in preparation stage."},payment:{question1:"What payment methods are available?",answer1:"We accept cash on delivery, credit card payment, and electronic payment through digital wallets.",question2:"Is payment secure?",answer2:"Yes, all payment transactions are protected with advanced encryption technologies to ensure the security of your financial information."},technical:{question1:"The app is not working properly, what should I do?",answer1:"Try restarting the app first, and if the problem persists, make sure to update the app to the latest version, or contact our technical support team.",question2:"How can I update the app?",answer2:"You can update the app through the app store (App Store or Google Play) and search for the app, then click \"Update\" if available."}},notifications:{header:"Notifications",showAll:"Show All",unreadOnly:"Unread Only",markAllRead:"Mark All as Read",noNotifications:"No notifications",newOrder:"New Order",newOrderMessage:"New order received from Al-Salam Hospital",followUpReminder:"Follow-up Reminder",followUpMessage:"Follow up on King Fahd Hospital order before end of day",inventoryUpdate:"Inventory Update",inventoryMessage:"Medical equipment inventory updated successfully",clientMeeting:"Client Meeting",meetingMessage:"You have a meeting with Al-Markaz Specialist Hospital representative tomorrow at 10 AM",specialOffer:"Special Offer",offerMessage:"Special offer on X-ray equipment for limited time",timeAgo:{minutes:"minutes ago",hours:"hours ago",days:"days ago"},filterUnread:"Filter Unread"},reportsScreen:{header:"Report",selectCity:"Select City",selectArea:"Select Area",from:"From",to:"To",selectStartDate:"Select start date",selectEndDate:"Select end date"},tableHeaders:{name:"Name",sales:"Sales",target:"Target",achievement:"Achievement",region:"Region",performance:"Performance",bonus:"Bonus"},achievementStatus:{achieved:"Achieved",exceeded:"Exceeded",noc:"NOC"},locations:{cities:{amman:"Amman",zarqa:"Zarqa",irbid:"Irbid",aqaba:"Aqaba"},areas:{amman:{alAbdali:"AlAbdali",sweifieh:"Sweifieh",jabalAmman:"Jabal Amman",tlaaAlAli:"Tlaa Al-Ali"},zarqa:{